Instructions:
Download NoviceHelper_UpdateSite zip, unzip and put this into an easily reachable location
in Eclipse Help > Install new software > Add... > Local... > (PATH TO NOVICEHELPER_UPDATESITE FOLDER) > Open > Checkbox
for NoviceHelper_Feature > finish

(restart Eclipse)

Window > Show View > Other > Other > Novice Error View > (drag so both Problems View and Error View can be shown)

